lead_paragraph: Saudi Arabia-based retail chain Jarir Bookstore has removed books written by U.S. presidential candidate Donald Trump from its shelves, it said on Tuesday, part of a backlash against his proposal to stop Muslims from entering the United States.

headline.main: Saudi Bookstore Pulls Trump Books From Shelves
